    "The final results of the proposed network were calculated as the mean and standard deviation of these experiments.In order to assess the efficacy of our proposed model, we utilize both the confusion matrix and overall accuracy measures.",
    "Through the use of the confusion matrix, discrepancies between predicted and true labels can be easily identified.Overall accuracy, on the other hand, is a measure of the ratio of correctly predicted values to the total number of predicted values across all test sets.",
    "This metric provides an evaluation of the model's performance in accurately classifying data.",
    "Experimental detailsThe proposed model discussed in this article has been implemented using the Tensorflow framework.",
    "During our experimentation, we set the training epoch to 500 and each epoch has a batch size of 4."
